                <li>A laser lightening/pigmentation treatment is performed with an extraordinary nanosecond laser (Q-switched/Quasi long).</li>
                <li>It is not a painful treatment but anesthetizing the area can be done as requested with the use of topical cosmetic cream. </li>
                <li>Each sitting requires merely 10 to 20 minutes.</li>
